spec_data.Name: php-nikic-php-parser3
spec_data.Description:
This is a PHP 5.2 to PHP 7.1 parser written in PHP.
Its purpose is to simplify static code analysis and manipulation.

This package provides the library version 3 and the php-parse3 command.

Documentation: https://github.com/nikic/PHP-Parser/tree/master/doc

Autoloader: /usr/share/php/PhpParser3/autoload.php

spec_data.Summary: A PHP parser written in PHP
